data.title: Joe E. Brown and granddaughter, Cynthia Lee Brown
data.meta_description: Title supplied by cataloger.Pictured are film comedian, Joe E. Brown, escorting his granddaughter, Cynthia Lee Brown, daughter of Joe L. Brown Jr., to an unidentified event. Photograph dated December 30, 1953.
